terms.medium_def:
A location first mentioned at Num.32.8; 
referred to as Kadesh (קָדֵשׁ), or Kedesh (קֶ֫דֶשׁ), or Kadesh-barnea (NIV= Kadesh Barnea) (קָדֵשׁ בַּרְנֵעַ), or En-mishpat (NIV= En Mishpat) (עֵין מִשְׁפָּט). § a city in the extreme south of Judah
same as 'Kedesh' and 'Kadesh-barnea'

